quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,When the earth is quaked with its quaking
  99,2,and the earth brings out its weighty material
  99,3,"and man will say, “What ails her ?”"
  99,4,She will be made to tell her news on that day
  99,5,because your Lord (would have) communicated to her
  99,6,"On that day human beings will be brought forth in diverse groups, to be shown their deeds"
  99,7,"So whoever does good equivalent in weight, even to a small particle, will see it"
  99,8,"And whoever does evil equivalent in weight, even to a small particle, will see it"